{
  "chapter": 9,
  "chapter_summary": "第九回「邪恶的欲望」摘要\n\n小马一行人在狼山上遭遇夜狼连续袭击，常无意亮出软剑迎战，以眉心暗器夺命追魂，杀退大批夜狼后跛足黑衣人下令撤退。香香中迷香昏迷，众人伤疲交加却仍坚持前进，小马主动抬轿鼓舞士气。蓝兰向小马表白心意却被他沉默回应。跛足黑衣人再次出现占据险要岩石，珍珠姐妹冲动冲向敌人被常无意拦下。黎明前鸡啼响起，远方传来朝拜太阳的神秘乐声，夜狼被迫撤退。三个神秘朝拜者现身——美腿少女直白向小马表白邀他同行，蓝兰争风相对；长发少年解释他们朝拜太阳的信仰。另一神秘少女以魔力般的眼神迷住珍珠姐妹，留下诱惑之语后离去。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "扎好伤势，就立刻向前闯。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zeng_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "曾珍",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "我们总该先休息一阵子。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_zeng_zhen",
      "text": "你着想死，尽管一个人留下来。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "轿夫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老牛伤得很重，就算还能向前走，也没法子抬轿子了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有病的人并不一定要坐轿子的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "一定要坐。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "你没有腿？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "那么你为何不能自己走？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "因为我就算自己下来走，这顶轿子也不能留下来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "其实这根本不成问题，只要是人，就会抬轿子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_pi",
      "speaker_name": "老皮",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "我不会。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_lao_pi",
      "text": "你可以学。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_pi",
      "speaker_name": "老皮",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "我以后一定会去学。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_lao_pi",
      "text": "用不着等到以后，你现在就可以学，而且我保证你一学就会。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_pi",
      "speaker_name": "老皮",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "难道你想要我抬轿子？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_lao_pi",
      "text": "你不抬谁抬？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_pi",
      "speaker_name": "老皮",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "好，你叫我抬，我就抬，谁叫我们是老朋友呢？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_lao_pi",
      "text": "有时候我实在觉得你这人不但聪明，而且可爱。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_pi",
      "speaker_name": "老皮",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "只可惜你是个男的，否则……",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "跛足的黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "退。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "香香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他…，他们会不会再来？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_zhang_long_zi",
      "text": "她并没有死，只不过中了迷香。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_long_zi",
      "speaker_name": "张聋子",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "刚才明明看见小马第一个就已将那个用迷香的人击倒，还踏碎了他的述香筒，她怎么会被迷倒的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_zhang_long_zi",
      "text": "你为什么不问她自己？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_long_zi",
      "speaker_name": "张聋子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁知道她中的是哪种迷香？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhang_long_zi",
      "text": "是种无药可解的迷香！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhang_long_zi",
      "text": "幸好她中的并不深，绝不会死的！",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是那些人若是再来，她就死定了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_pi",
      "speaker_name": "老皮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那群狼若是再来，不但她死了，我们只怕都死定了！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_lao_pi",
      "text": "可是他们死的一定更多。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zeng_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "曾珍",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也许他们的人已经快死光，已不会再来！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zeng_zhen",
      "text": "也许！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_pi",
      "speaker_name": "老皮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也许他们马上就会再来！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_lao_pi",
      "text": "你为什么总是喜欢说让人讨厌的话！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_pi",
      "speaker_name": "老皮",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "因为我不说别人也一样讨厌我！",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在我才知道，狼山真是个可怕的地方！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我倒看不出这地方有他妈的什么可怕？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你看不出？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "我只看得出他们已快死光了，我们却还全部都活着！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在大家还能不能往前走？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "为什么不能？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大家的腿都没有断，没有不能往前走的！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_pi",
      "speaker_name": "老皮",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "可是我……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_lao_pi",
      "text": "我知道你受了伤，你不能抬轿子，我抬！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "看样子他们已不会再来了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "可是我们总得找个地方休息林息，否则大家都没法子再支持下去。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "当然除了你，你简直好象是个铁打的人。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "假如我嫁给你，你要不要？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "难道你还想着她？她究竟是个什么样的女人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "是闯过去，还是停下来？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zeng_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "曾珍",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只想宰了那王八蛋！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zeng_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "曾珠",
      "listener": "char_zeng_zhen",
      "text": "你还能宰人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zeng_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "曾珍",
      "listener": "char_zeng_zhu",
      "text": "能！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zeng_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "曾珠",
      "listener": "char_zeng_zhen",
      "text": "我们去不去宰？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zeng_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "曾珍",
      "listener": "char_zeng_zhu",
      "text": "去！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zeng_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "曾珠",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "你想干什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zeng_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "曾珍",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "你是不是有毛病？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "跛足的黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "你一定有毛病。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "跛足的黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "你救了她们，她们反而骂你。没有毛病的人，怎么会做这种事？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "跛足的黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "其实你救不救她们都一样，反正你们都死定了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你有手，为什么不自己下来跟我动手？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "跛足的黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "因为我不必。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "跛足的黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "你的剑很快。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "跛足的黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "而且你有把好剑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "跛足的黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "抬轿子的那小伙子的拳头好像也是双好拳头。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "跛足的黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是我的兄弟们，却还想再试试你们的快剑和拳头。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zeng_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "曾珍",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在他无论多么凶，我都不怕了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zeng_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "曾珠",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为现在我们已知道，他那副凶样子，只不过故意装出来给别人看的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他的脸虽冷，一颗心却是热的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你好象也跟他差不多。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既然大家都还没有死，腿也没有断，为什么不往前走？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 484
    },
