      "speaker_name": "长发少年",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "今天我们的朝拜祭礼比平时提早了些。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 612,
      "line_end": 612
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_chang_fa_shao_nian",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 614,
      "line_end": 614
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_fa_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "长发少年",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "因为她喜欢你。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 616,
      "line_end": 616
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_mei_tui_de_shao_nv",
      "text": "就算是你救了我们，他也不会跟你走的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 624,
      "line_end": 624
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_tui_de_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "美腿的少女",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "你呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 626,
      "line_end": 626
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_mei_tui_de_shao_nv",
      "text": "这里没有人会跟你走。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 628,
      "line_end": 628
    },
    {
